longBusinessSummary: Empower Clinics Inc., an integrated healthcare company, provides body and mind wellness services for patients through its clinics, with digital and telemedicine care, and medical diagnostics laboratories in North America. It offers preventative, diagnostic, and treatment services that focuses on patient experience. The company is based in Vancouver, Canada.
